See the [regex demo][1]. It matches:

 - `@\[` - a `@[` char sequence
 - `([^\][]+)` - Group 1: any one or more chars other than `]` and `[` 
 - `]\(` - a `](` substring
 - `(\d+)` - Group 2: one or more digits
